### ERROR TIPS
### Trying to place an entity without having it in inventory
- Before attempting to place an entity, ensure that the entity is present in the agent's inventory.

### Trying to insert items when the agent does not have them in inventory
- Before attempting to insert items into an entity, ensure that the agent has the required items in its inventory.
